			<h1><s:property value="messages.h1Title"/></h1>
			<p>Beginning January 15 through April 7, 2024, players have the chance to turn their non-winning multiplier-themed Scratch-Off tickets from the
			new X THE CASH family into extra opportunities for cash prizes through the Xtreme Cash Bonus Play! A total of four drawings will be held to award more
			than $500,000 in prizes, including the chance to win cash prizes of up to $20,000!</p>
			
			<p>In each entry period, players will earn draw entries equal to the price of the ticket entered. In addition, players who enter the complete non-winning
			X THE CASH family of Scratch-Off tickets ($1, $2, $5, $10, and $50) during the same entry period will receive 100 bonus entries. These bonus entries are awarded for each
			completed set of X THE CASH family of Scratch-Off tickets.</p>	
			<p>Players entering the new, non-winning 500X THE CASH Scratch-Off ticket can instantly win a $100 coupon.</p>
		
		
